Interface SearchCriteria

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    And, ContactField, NonNull, Or, Regex

    public interface SearchCriteria
    Author:
    shenli

    A class can implement the SearchCriteria interface when it wants to impose a searching criteria on the objects.

      • matchCondition

        boolean matchCondition(ContactEntry element)
        This method is called whenever checking the object is matched the specified condition. Returns true if the element matches the specified condition, otherwise false.

        Returns:
        true if the element matches the specified condition, otherwise false
